  "description": "<p>Job Highlights</p><ul><li>Competitive Remuneration Package</li><li>Work Life Balance & Positive Culture with Positive Vibes</li><li>Immediate Hiring & Full-Time Permanent Job Role</li></ul><p>Job Description</p><ul><li>Assists in department daily routine.</li><li>Handle data entry and clerical duties.</li><li>Perform good customer service.</li><li>Perform stock control and follow up on office maintenance.</li><li>Answer telephone calls in a professional and courteous manner</li><li>Ad hoc duties that are assigned from time to time.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Entry level candidates are welcome</li><li>Minimum GCE 'O' Levels or ITE / Diploma / Professional Certification in Administration are welcome to apply.</li><li>Willing to learn with good attitude.</li><li>Computer literate.</li><li>Organized and responsible.</li><li>Able to speak English fluently in order to assist and communicate with clients.</li><li>Strong sales and admin track record will be advantage.</li><li>Team player who is able to manage task independently with minimum supervision.</li><li>Possess good inter-personal and marketing skills.</li><li>Candidates with at least 1 to 2 years experience has an added advantage,</li><li>Singaporeans are welcome to apply, and quota available.</li><li>Salary will be commensurate based on experience and qualifications.</li></ul>",
